  "detailed_description": "Warning: Please take caution if you have problems with seizures or similar issues! This game features many flashing bright lights!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477310/extras/97861b20837991568b741e3687eefcfe.poster.avif?t=1708123152\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477310/extras/97861b20837991568b741e3687eefcfe.webm?t=1708123152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477310/extras/97861b20837991568b741e3687eefcfe.mp4?t=1708123152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Will you enter the SPACE HOLE?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477310/extras/9dd2f60e2b6827cc540c3e84b78ef562.poster.avif?t=1708123152\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477310/extras/9dd2f60e2b6827cc540c3e84b78ef562.webm?t=1708123152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477310/extras/9dd2f60e2b6827cc540c3e84b78ef562.mp4?t=1708123152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Can you traverse the LEVELS?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477310/extras/72c8ca8f10a1d4a268779ac5f40a294f.poster.avif?t=1708123152\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477310/extras/72c8ca8f10a1d4a268779ac5f40a294f.webm?t=1708123152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477310/extras/72c8ca8f10a1d4a268779ac5f40a294f.mp4?t=1708123152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>SPACE HOLE is a silly and or bouncy interpretation of Super Monkey Ball; but in the Mysterious Space. A single-player adventure through over 100 levels, split into hubs like Hell and the Eyeballs Dimension.  Levels are bite-sized and arcadey, with an overall run time around 2 or 3 hours.<br><br>In the near future, humans discover the missing piece for faster-than-light travel: giant glass spheres.<br>All we needed to break the light-barrier was the light-ball... and now we've done it.<br>Alone in your capsule, you venture into the deepest reaches of Space... through the SPACE HOLE.<br><br>Music is from Beverly Crusher's Cheeseburger Liquor Party (2015) and Pills Pills Pills (2016).<br><br>Supports gamepad (eg Xbox 360 pad) or mouse & keyboard!<br>Graphical settings that will work for most computers!",
  "about_the_game": "Warning: Please take caution if you have problems with seizures or similar issues! This game features many flashing bright lights!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477310/extras/97861b20837991568b741e3687eefcfe.poster.avif?t=1708123152\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477310/extras/97861b20837991568b741e3687eefcfe.webm?t=1708123152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477310/extras/97861b20837991568b741e3687eefcfe.mp4?t=1708123152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Will you enter the SPACE HOLE?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477310/extras/9dd2f60e2b6827cc540c3e84b78ef562.poster.avif?t=1708123152\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477310/extras/9dd2f60e2b6827cc540c3e84b78ef562.webm?t=1708123152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477310/extras/9dd2f60e2b6827cc540c3e84b78ef562.mp4?t=1708123152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Can you traverse the LEVELS?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477310/extras/72c8ca8f10a1d4a268779ac5f40a294f.poster.avif?t=1708123152\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477310/extras/72c8ca8f10a1d4a268779ac5f40a294f.webm?t=1708123152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477310/extras/72c8ca8f10a1d4a268779ac5f40a294f.mp4?t=1708123152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>SPACE HOLE is a silly and or bouncy interpretation of Super Monkey Ball; but in the Mysterious Space. A single-player adventure through over 100 levels, split into hubs like Hell and the Eyeballs Dimension.  Levels are bite-sized and arcadey, with an overall run time around 2 or 3 hours.<br><br>In the near future, humans discover the missing piece for faster-than-light travel: giant glass spheres.<br>All we needed to break the light-barrier was the light-ball... and now we've done it.<br>Alone in your capsule, you venture into the deepest reaches of Space... through the SPACE HOLE.<br><br>Music is from Beverly Crusher's Cheeseburger Liquor Party (2015) and Pills Pills Pills (2016).<br><br>Supports gamepad (eg Xbox 360 pad) or mouse & keyboard!<br>Graphical settings that will work for most computers!",
